import BarraNavegacao from "../nav/BarraNavegacao"
import HomePage from "../homepage/HomePage"
import Carrinho from "../carrinho/Carrinho"
import { MainStyle } from "./style"
import { useState } from "react"


function Main (){

    const [botaoCamiseta, setBotaoCamiseta] =useState

    return(
        <MainStyle>
            <BarraNavegacao/>
            <HomePage botaoCamiseta={botaoCamiseta} setBotaoCamiseta={setBotaoCamiseta}/>
            <Carrinho/>
        </MainStyle>
    )
}

export default Main
